SUMMARY:Mambo City-Salsa Fridays
DESCRIPTION:Mambo City Salsa Friday \n* 1. Dedicated room playing Salsa\n* Top DJs & Instructors\n* Beautiful wooden dance floor\n* spacious venue\n* You can bring your own drinks-No Bar\n* Plenty of free parking after 6.30pm\n* No congestion zone\n* Salsa social \n★The Schedule★\nSalsa Room:\nClasses with Mambo City Team & Guest…….\nTeaching \n3 Levels \nInt/Adv. \n– TBA-Int/Adv Salsa on1\nImprovers – Robert -Salsa on1\nBeginners – Mambo City Team-Salsa on1 “Mambo City Team” \nDJs: TBA & Cruz (Bobby Blanco) \nDoors Open: 8pm-1am\nSalsa classes@8.15pm\nBeginners\, Improvers and Int/Adv\nDancing until 1am\nWe will be keeping the music playing as you dance 💃 🕺all night long!! \nPrice:\nAdvance Tickets: £12 via Eventbrite \nOn the door: £15/£12 Members/£10 NUS/NHS\nGet your advanced discounted tickets:\nVia Eventbrite www.MamboCity.co.uk \nAddress:\nMarlborough School\nDraycott Ave\nChelsea\nLondon\nSW3 3AP \nDriving:\nPlenty of Street Parking after 6:30pm\nWe are outside of the congestion zone\nPublic Transport \nNearest Bus Stop is less than 100 Metres\, Buses: 319\, 22\, 11\, 137\nNearest Tube Station: South Kensington\nDistrict\, Circle and Piccadilly lines. \nAttention:\nOur venue would like us to help protect the dance floor\, should you dance in heels\, especially stilettos you will need to wear heel protectors. \nThe use of talc powder is strictly prohibited\n🚫 and caused damage to the beautiful floor.\nIt is not necessary\, it is a really fast floor\, if you have any questions please inbox us. \nHand Sanitisers still avail \nWe do not operate a Bar at this venue\,\nYou can bring your own drinks and bottle/container in order to refill at the tap..\nThere is a Sainsbury’s nearby. \nLimited Complimentary Teas & Coffee and some snacks \nTo be notified … Join Mambo City fans page on fb or follow MamboCityuk on Instagram or join our mailing list www.MamboCity.co.uk \n2026 full dates\non the website\nFri 20th Feb ✔️\nFri 20th Mar ✔️\nFri 17th April ✔️\nFri 15th May ✔️\nFri 17th July ✔️\nFri 18th Sept ✔️\nFri 16th Oct ✔️\nFri 20th Nov ✔️\nFri 18th Dec ✔️ \nMamboCity Glamour & Glitz\nSat 26th Dec (End of Year)
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/mambo-city-salsa-fridays-2/2026-03-20/
CATEGORIES:London
END:VEVENT
