SUMMARY:Third Friday Cuban Salsa Classes and Party
DESCRIPTION:RCR’s weekly Friday classes and Cuban Salsa Dance Party are at Mars Bar once a month\, every 3rd Friday.\nWe will now be offering three levels of classes at each hour at Mars\, just like we do at MNC on the 1st\, 2nd\, 4th\, and 5th Fridays.\nBeginners are always welcome in any Level 1 class — couples or singles (no partner necessary). Here’s the schedule:\n6:00 – 7:00pm Cuban Salsa & Rueda (Level 1)\n6:00 – 7:00pm Cuban Salsa & Rueda (Level 3)\n6:00 – 7:00pm Cuban Salsa & Rueda (Level 4)\n7:15 – 8:15pm Cuban Salsa & Rueda (Level 2)\n7:15 – 8:15pm Cuban Salsa & Rueda (Level 3)\n7:15 – 8:15pm Cuban Salsa & Rueda (Level 4)\n8:15 – 11:00pm Open dancing with DJ Ritmo — free with any class\, otherwise $5 – 10 (sliding scale\, cash or Venmo)\nWe will still be offering our regular 7:30pm class at ODC (free admission to Mars Bar afterwards).
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/third-friday-cuban-salsa-classes-and-party/2026-03-20/
LOCATION:Mars Bar San Francisco\, 798 Brannan St\, San Francisco\, CA\, 94103\, United States
CATEGORIES:San Francisco
GEO:37.7732647;-122.4031788
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Mars Bar San Francisco 798 Brannan St San Francisco CA 94103 United States;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=798 Brannan St:geo:-122.4031788,37.7732647
END:VEVENT
