SUMMARY:Son Montuno Presents: Buena Vista Social club tribute
DESCRIPTION:Feel the rhythm of live Latin music at The Delancey on Friday March 20 🎶 Get ready for a vibrant set filled with classic Cuban sounds\, rich percussion\, and irresistible grooves that will bring the spirit of Havana straight to the Lower East Side. If you love live music that makes you move\, this is a set you won’t want to miss.\n645pm Son Montuno\n@sonmontunonyc\nInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/sonmontunonyc/\nYouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@jelenacingara398\nBand Info: https://www.pianolessonsnyc.space/son-montuno-band\nhttps://www.instagram.com/sonmontunonyc/
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/son-montuno-presents-buena-vista-social-club-tribute-2/
LOCATION:Delancey\, 168 Delancey Street\, New york City\, NY\, 10002\, United States
CATEGORIES:New York City
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Sonmontuno.jpg-2.png
ORGANIZER;CN="jelena Cingara":MAILTO:jelenacingara@gmail.com
