SUMMARY:Salsa & Bachata y más! at Glen Echo Park - every third Friday of the month
DESCRIPTION:## DESCRIPTION ## \nGlen Echo Park Partnership for Arts & Culture presents Salsa & Bachata y más! Come experience sizzling hot Salsa and the magic of all styles of Bachata in this special night of Latin Dance.\nBut wait! There’s more! We’ll also dance Merengue\, Kizomba\, y más! \nJoin us every third Friday of the month in the Ballroom Back Room for a night of connection and pure dance bliss. Whether you’re a seasoned pro or taking your first steps\, our vibrant community will welcome you with open arms (and smooth moves). Expect friendly faces and effortless connection; No partner? No problem! We rotate partners and foster a warm\, inclusive atmosphere. All levels welcome! \nMonthly\, on the third Friday of the month! \n## SCHEDULE ##\n– 7:30pm – 8:15pm: Open Level Salsa Lesson\n– 8:15pm – 9:00pm: Open Level Bachata Lesson\n– 9:00pm – 11:30pm: Dancing with DJ \n## TICKETS ##\n– Discounted Advance Tickets ($15) || Online Only || Sales end at 11:59pm the night before the dance\n– Same-Day Tickets ($18) || Online or at the door (Cash\, Check\, or Credit Card) \n## PARKING ##\n– Use the following address for GPS to take you to our FREE parking lot: 5801 Oxford Road\, Glen Echo\, MD 20812\n– For Google Maps\, search “Glen Echo Park Parking”\n– Parking & Directions: glenechopark.org/directions || Park Map: glenechopark.org/parkmap
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/salsa-bachata-y-mas-at-glen-echo-park-every-third-friday-of-the-month/2026-03-20/
LOCATION:Glen Echo Park\, 7300 Macarthur Boulevard\,\, Glen Echo\, MD\, 20812\, United States
CATEGORIES:Washington DC-Baltimore
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Salsa-Bachata-y-mas-Square-Image.png
END:VEVENT
