SUMMARY:The Latin Quarter
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to The LATIN QUARTER – Sydney’s Premier Monthly and Pop-Up Bachata Party!\nJoin Sydney’s best Latin dancers on the dance floor at The Latin Quarter!\nOFF Broadway Hotel is a idea-located venue with a great atmosphere\, food & drink and plenty of room to execute all your favourite dance moves.\n100% Bachata Music by Host DJS – DJ Whisperer\, DJ M.I.A + Friends playing the most current and popular songs of the moment.\nSee page events for details or contact us directly.\nAddress:\nOFF Broadway Hotel\n31-33 Bay Street\nUltimo NSW 2037\nCONTACT DETAILS\nMitch Mobile: +61411445969\nTony Mobile: +61414000567\nEmail: dance@dwmsydney.com.au\nSocial Media\nFacebook: thelatinquartersydney\nInstagram: thelatinquartersydney
