SUMMARY:La Fiesta - Bachata Fever Friday Night Social Dancing
DESCRIPTION:“La Fiesta Friday night social dancing” presented by Bachata Fever Dance.\nYour favorite party time at La Bodega! As usual it is a FREE entry event.\nDrawing inspiration from the parties of the Caribbean\, come down and explore some amazing Latin music and delicious food.\nEvent details:\nComplimentary Dominican Bachata dance class from 8pm – 9pm.\nSocial dancing from 9pm – 1am with guest DJs spinning amazing Latin music Bachata\, Salsa\, Merengue\, Kizomba and Cumbia…\nDirections: LA BODEGA\, Shop 1\, 12 Fitzroy Street\, St. Kilda (the colourful Lego fence next to Pizza Hut). Ample parking in the area. (Park Street\, Mary Street\, Loch Street)\nPublic transport via trams 96 or 16 stop at Jacka Boulevard\, tram 12 stop at Fitzroy Street.\nSee you on the dance floor!
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/la-fiesta-bachata-fever-friday-night-social-dancing-2-2/2026-03-20/
LOCATION:La Bodega\, 12 Fitzroy street\, Melbourne\, VIC\, 3182\, Australia
CATEGORIES:Melbourne
