SUMMARY:Controla Fridays
DESCRIPTION:Hola familia! Come join us every first and third Friday for Controla Fridays at the beautiful Pivot Ballroom in the suburbs of Philadelphia!\nLocation: Pivot Ballroom\n49 E. Lancaster Ave. Ardmore\, PA\n(only 20 min from center city Phila)\nFeaturing:\nWorkshops with guest artists (doors open at 7:45pm)\n-3 awesome Djs playing the hottest salsa & bachata 10pm-1am\n-Our awesome #ControlaFam vibing with all of us all night\n-Beautiful spacious venue with great floor for dancing in the Philly suburbs\n-Free parking available\n-Free food & water\n-Event is BYOB\n-Our #ControlaCam capturing behind the scenes so dress to impress\, and so much MORE for still ONLY $20 OR come early before 10pm and only pay $15!\nYou know we always try our best to bring you the most bang for your buck.\nSo pls help us spread the word\,\ncome join us\, save us all a dance\, and see you there this Friday.
